  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">AS 4349.3 standard &middot; settlement-grade report</span>
      <h1>Pre-purchase termite inspection across <span class="accent">Greater Darwin</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Buying a home in the Top End? Don&rsquo;t settle without an
        AS 4349.3 inspection. We find active termite evidence or significant
        past damage in roughly 18&ndash;22% of Darwin pre-purchase inspections
        on pre-1990 stock, and 8&ndash;12% on newer slab-on-ground &mdash;
        almost always undisclosed by the seller. Written report for your
        conveyancer within 24 hours. ~$480&ndash;$680 standard urban residential;
        $580&ndash;$950 for rural Litchfield acreage. Best $600 you&rsquo;ll
        ever spend on a Top End property purchase.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book an inspection</a>
